txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Monstrous goo from the insects surrounding the outpost of Gwingris. You can return the items to Maedlathron at Gwingris in Eregion for reward.
'I will send this on to be studied by our scholars. Thank you.'
'We must identify everything that has infested these lands. I require a collection of filth and carapaces from the insects in these lands.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Monstrous Goo
Maedlathron awaits the return of a collection of monstrous goo at the Elf-encampment at Gwingris.
Deliver the monstrous goo to Maedlathron in Gwingris within Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver monstrous goo from the insects near and surrounding the Elf-encampment of Gwingris to the Elf Maedlathron.
Wanted: Monstrous goo from the insects surrounding the outpost of Gwingris.
